{"type": "article", "id": 2426, "title": "纯手作明信片套装", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-18T07:52:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004215Zm9erW2ODtA6Ykw5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t不少人在旅途当中都有邮寄明信片给亲朋好友的习惯，最近日本设计师 Eiko Nagase 与 Tomomi Sasaki 设计了一组明信片套装，或可成为你的最佳旅伴。这款套装选用了毛毡材质，由纯手工制作完成。它类似于一个小型的紧凑工具包，内部设计有专门放置明显片的空间，此外还配有两个小型口袋，提供海军蓝、灰色以及绿色 3 色可选，定价 15 美元，<a href=\"http://shop.spoon-tamago.com/collections/stationery/products/felt-postcard-kit\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004213ZXjWeiMwOUIQs7C2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004214eDTv5tZuRjaYiHJ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004214n2IhsF8YWCZcfGXx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}